videos.headline: Michigan's Maddie Nolan drains the three
videos.description: Emily Kiser crashes the offensive glass, leading to an easy second-chance three-pointer for Maddie Nolan.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Michigan's Maddie Nolan drains the three) 2023/01/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Penn State's Makenna Marisa turns a steal into a bucket
videos.description: Makenna Marisa jumps into the passing lane for the steal and hits a fall-away jumper on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Penn State's Makenna Marisa turns a steal into a bucket) 2023/01/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Michigan's Leigha Brown shows off her court vision
videos.description: Leigha Brown launches a long pass down court to find Maddie Nolan for an easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Michigan's Leigha Brown shows off her court vision) 2023/01/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Michigan's Maddie Nolan with a nice chase-down block
videos.description: Maddie Nolan stops a Penn State fast break with an athletic chase-down block.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Michigan's Maddie Nolan with a nice chase-down block) 2023/01/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Michigan's Leigha Brown converts an and-1
videos.description: A steal by Emily Kiser turns into a tough Leigha Brown and-1 finish on the other end.

videos.headline: Penn State's Leilani Kapinus finishes an acrobatic layup
videos.description: Leilani Kapinus drives and spins through the lane to finish a layup to extend the Lady Lions' lead.
